{"tid":220693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦冀港人尊重國家制度 存敬畏之心","createTime":"2017-04-28T06:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T08:26:46.000Z","uid":30404,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"649cdee8ec5f81439df03776c7b473432991410d","tid":220693,"uid":30404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"中聯辦法律部部長王振民在一個研討會上致辭時表示，香港回歸以來，<span style=\"color: red;\">中央給予最大程度的照顧</span>，政治和法律體系的磨合大致上成功，只是有少數人不願意面對回歸的政治現實。<br />\n<br />\n王振民稱，回歸以來，香港的法治、人權、自由無被削弱，但中國在香港受到的待遇反而不及歐美國家，香港辱罵中國的制度亦是最厲害。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，國家用數十年建立現行制度，為了香港回歸，在政治和法律上進行許多補充修改，但制度不能因香港回歸而全盤推翻，冀港人嘗試理解國家邏輯和道理，<span style=\"color: red;\">對國家的制度有基本尊重及<span style=\"font-size: large;\">敬畏之心</span></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/04/28/1552778_0ddb1c31bd6f9ec55d7fe86fd0eb1b16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F1552778_0ddb1c31bd6f9ec55d7fe86fd0eb1b16.png&h=46fac54c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要感恩呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd86a86c6b10e85858efcc30d2f424453270876","tid":220693,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母死共狗"},{"pid":"704ef1b138e2248df754a44c88ae088c1a34f5d2","tid":220693,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"香港嘈你中國呢個邪惡國家最多, 係因為香港食最多中國嘅屎嘛<br />\n件垃圾講嘢都唔用腦"},{"pid":"4cf9ef80b33204a3ede9bdbbf74e724ecaaa537f","tid":220693,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:21:34.000Z","msg":"中國給予香港最大程度照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係知97之後香港全方面倒退緊"},{"pid":"7021f66e39e6757d706d18b4a7398ee37b66a4d8","tid":220693,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:23:44.000Z","msg":